      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine is reliable and starts without issue, though there is a slight, non-critical oil leak that will eventually need attention. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, and the interior shows typical wear and tear, including a small tear in the driver's seat. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done for a fair price.",
