    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously preserved vehicle, currently offered in showroom condition. This unit has been maintained to an uncompromising standard, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. A rare find for the serious enthusiast, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, offering both mechanical excellence and aesthetic perfection. We invite you to experience a level of refinement that is truly peerless within the secondary market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
