    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This chassis has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and preventive rod bearing service, ensuring mechanical longevity. The suspension geometry remains true, featuring aluminum control arms and MacPherson struts that offer surgical turn-in. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is exceptional and the interior bolsters show zero wear. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
